  "id": "CENTRAL-OSHWC",
  "name": "Occupational Safety, Health and Working Conditions Code, 2020",
  "shortName": "OSHWC Code",
  "officialCitation": "The Occupational Safety, Health and Working Conditions Code, 2020 (Act No. 37 of 2020), operative from 21 November 2025.",
  "overview": "The Occupational Safety, Health and Working Conditions Code, 2020 is the current central framework for establishment registration, occupational safety and health, welfare, working hours and leave, women employees, contract labour, inter-State migrant workers and sector-specific working conditions. It became operative on 21 November 2025. The 2026 Central Rules apply where the Central Government is the appropriate government; State and Union Territory rules apply elsewhere. Instruments under the thirteen repealed enactments continue only to the extent preserved by section 143.",
